title: 5 reasons why Australia should be wary of Virat Kohli's invincibles
text:
5 reasons why Australia should be wary of Virat Kohli's invincibles IndiaToday.in | February 22, 2017 SYL canal row: Supreme Court says enough is enough, Punjab must execute treaty Embed Feedback 
India and Australia square off in a four-Test series from February 23. What are the major challenges for the visitors against Kohli's iInvincibles? Is it just the spinners or the turning tracks. 
We give you give good reasons Australia should be mighty worried over the next few weeks of their India tour. Watch Right Now
